That place has the worst public order, like a hangout for

"It's absolutely unthinkable under normal circumstances...

"There's always a chance of something happening, so maybe I
should go check it out... If Makoto is in the neighboring
town, I need to hurry and bring her back..."

"What a filthy town... The rumors seem to be true... I can't
stay here long. I need to find Makoto quickly..."

"Makoto... you walk too fast... not even caring about the
rain, just moving forward..."

"But this time, I somehow managed not to lose sight of
you... It seems Makoto went into this factory..."

"My body is completely soaked... I need to find Makoto
quickly and get back home."

"Makoto must be somewhere in this factory... For starters, I
guess I'll search everywhere."
